SAMUEL JOHNSON (Coffee House) COGNAC 6.77

It is entirely appropriate for this excellent "Grande Fine Champagne Cognac" to be named in Dr. Samuel Johnson's honor since he is the one who said, "Claret is the drink for boys; port is the drink for men; but he who aspires to be a Hero must drink Brandy!"
